comments: This is very simple. It shows an availability calendar for a month. Clicking on a cell shows a modal with the number of beds available. The divs with id "giorno<day>" show the number of beds available.

comments: - [ ] 15 day calendar with for each bed type the yes/no availability of a given date. - [ ] Upon closer inspection on the day itself, you get more information + number of availability. Scraping can be done in a two-tier fashion (high-level first then closer look).
